===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪn|-aɪn]]

===Verb===

'''to opine'''

#To state as an opinion.

In order to express one's opinion you must opine. 

I had to opine on the situation because I thought a different perspective was in order.

